{"tid":2215768,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★亮點】花旗銀行\"透過電話隨機訪問\" 本港千萬富翁50.4萬人","createTime":"2020-09-24T08:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T14:58:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cf0b1c4433d994b1ed8bf7b687d3faffdf38504c","tid":2215768,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:03:21.000Z","msg":"花旗銀行公布「2019/2020年香港千萬富翁調查報告」顯示，截至今年5月，推算全港有50.4萬人擁有1000萬港元或以上淨資產，比2018年51.1萬人的紀錄高位減少1.4%，但比去年則回升22%。<br />\n<br />\n調查在去年11至12月，以及今年3至5月兩段期間進行，<span class=\"xx-large\">透過電話隨機訪問</span>超過3500名年齡介乎21至79歲的香港居民，千萬富翁佔本港相關年齡人口比例8.4%。當中，有56%的千萬富翁是男性，44%是女性。男性平均年齡58歲，而女性則是57歲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551197-20200923.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551197-20200923.htm&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFOF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=30e6cb65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551197-20200923.htm&h=a796fa83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551197-20200923.htm</a>"},{"pid":"deb3939a0217ff9c7a8802bc3b91902d15a0d6d8","tid":2215768,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:03:45.000Z","msg":"電話隨機訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024bad52b0d02297d2a3bd35022330d33cb7d1c8","tid":2215768,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"香港搵錢根本好易."},{"pid":"7b174b81954d95b8831c6a9da83235ee85c20a04","tid":2215768,"uid":2267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"我都有過千億，清明嗰時"},{"pid":"5b2d3a1bfff571db1dfdd06fa11f7bd2483b5598","tid":221